pageProduct.name: Wagner Super Colostrum Chewable 200 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
Warnings

Always read the label; take only as directed.
Products containing bovine colostrum powder contain lactose and cow’s milk proteins.
This product is not suitable for use in children under the age of 12 months except on professional health advice.


Formulated without:
Gluten, wheat, egg, soy, artificial colours, artificial flavours, artificial sweeteners.

Ingredients

Each chewable tablet provides
Bovine colostrum powder   400mg
Equiv. Bovine immunoglobulin G  80mg
Contains lactose and sugars.

Directions

Chew 6 tablets daily with food or as directed by your healthcare professional
